<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a01"/><p id="pI01p0182a0101">造碑人比
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a02"/>丘僧弁選
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a03"/>年九十四
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a04"/>　　讚三
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a05"/>　　寶福
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a06"/>　　業碑
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a07"/>齊太師錄
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a08"/>尚書事彭
<lb ed="C I" n="0182a09"/>城王高浟</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b01"/><p id="pI01p0182b0101">聞夫開士弘教。至人崇道。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">嗟</unclear>三界之危苦。悼□生之□□。將欲□□□□。□□舟樑。勢位同於
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b02"/>脫屣。國城均於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">棄</unclear>唾。然則勇猛不息。非為獨善。感通<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">所</unclear>□。利□塵沙。是故大覺乘時。慈悲一切。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b03"/>持智炬於昏境。擊法鼓於<note n="0182001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01042;＝聾【史】</note><app n="0182001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01042;</rdg></app>俗。迷<note n="0182002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30980;＝邪【史】</note><app n="0182002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30980;</rdg></app>反正。黑暗<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">遷</unclear>明。應物有期。世雄示滅。運神功於忍土。布靈
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b04"/>&CB00528;於大千。雙樹嵐鞞之下。乃興妙塔。顯節涼臺之上。驗諸圖象。思崇真正。世有人焉。冥中見曉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b05"/>復鍾□覺。太師錄尚書事彭城王。峰峻鍾山。枝華寶樹。心薀天璞。器孕<note n="0182003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30928;＝全【史】</note><app n="0182003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">全</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30928;</rdg></app>才。懸明鏡以臨方。置
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b06"/>歸墟而受物。多藝遺姬旦之能。樹德蔑劉蒼之善。天之所縱。不獨人中。化金練石之方。時為陋
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b07"/>術外生。調微之義。仍謂蕨言。窮神逐變。探冥弘道。藻身法海。竦慮玄門。以皮肉為坏器。以性<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">命</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b08"/>為畫水。得寶藏於身<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">中</unclear>。識金珠於額上。曰者□<note n="0182004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07321;＝驂【史】</note><app n="0182004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">驂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07321;</rdg></app>北邁。作牧維城。屈跡行春風之恩。<note n="0182005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30771;＝局【史】</note><app n="0182005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">局</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30771;</rdg></app>道為<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">秋</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b09"/>駕之術。循□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">問</unclear>邑。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">褰</unclear>襜高<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">視</unclear>。爰有勝地。宿置伽藍。南望呼沱。漢騎蹈冰之所。北臨易水。燕臣<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">行</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b10"/>歌之蹤。界<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear>俠藪。躡野縈林。泄雲<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">濆</unclear>雨。□珠□□。以茲博敞。寔栖靈聖。於是輟駕委心。慇懃至
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b11"/>道。悵房廡之隳壞。恨欹闕之不工。爰慕五<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>。放□□之法。乃懷三<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">劉</unclear>。興鏤金之想。徘徊正念。意
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b12"/>在於斯。及謁帝文□。入牽人寶。星<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">火</unclear>數迴。攝心彌篤。□□家臣。逾存經紀。搜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">素</unclear>&CB00216;青碧之珍。伐
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b13"/>貞松<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">文</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">梓</unclear>之木。揆星<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">成</unclear>則。測日為准。架室□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">雙</unclear>林之下。構<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">尊</unclear>像毗舍之地。龍王愧巧。天帝<note n="0182006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00518;＝慚【史】</note><app n="0182006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00518;</rdg></app>工。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b14"/>懸如意於暗中。不勞燈炬。置炎光於鍑下。自然香食。至如琢龍次<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">玉</unclear>。摹立靈象。妙範合聖。奇相
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b15"/>通神。光絕金膏。明兼銀燭。成就等應見之容。圓滿<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">若</unclear>下生之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">狀</unclear>。□僧德眾。踵至如林。憑心正路。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b16"/>絕&CB00528;疑<note n="0182007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08051;＝網【史】</note><app n="0182007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">網</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08051;</rdg></app>。持法鉤以牽毒。流智水以銷煩。戒行周圓。衿神空淨。圍繞晝夜。讚嘆頂禮。香氣如臺。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b17"/>花浮成蓋。風林搖薄。生微妙之音。蓮<note n="0182008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30981;＝沼【史】</note><app n="0182008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">沼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30981;</rdg></app>環迴。發哀雅之韻。翻同天上駕御之<note n="0182009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31168;＝園【史】</note><app n="0182009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31168;</rdg></app>。鬱似人間花林
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b18"/>之窟。資父事君。奉<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">國</unclear>遺己。宣茲願力。上奉　皇家世祀。共圓□周。久隆基興。方地齊固。乘寶殿
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b19"/>以飛空。駕金輪而傍轉。珠囊不委。玉鏡皕u。蠢蠢□生。咸歸□覺。若夫一念小善。猶居忉利之
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b20"/>上。兩錢輕拖。仍成羅漢之果。況乃據<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>憂之土。立大乘之宅。業深金剛之海。功□□玉之山。歸
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b21"/>生生之福。出死死之苦。永銷煩惚。畢竟清涼。勒茲琬琰。弘此偈讚。其詞曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b22"/>迷路遙緬。欲境<note n="0182010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30983;＝遼【史】</note><app n="0182010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30983;</rdg></app>闊。輪轉無窮。環循不脫。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">性</unclear>猶狂<note n="0182011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07782;＝象【史】</note><app n="0182011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07782;</rdg></app>。命同聚沫。毒箭傍侵。風刀下割。無名至道。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b23"/>權應時來。一音所說。万路咸開。人天迴向。魔梵俱摧。永懷寂滅。言昇妙臺。棺踊金色。林成鵠變。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b24"/><note n="0182012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30988;＝寶【史】</note><app n="0182012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寶</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30988;</rdg></app>聚常湛。三乘東轉。&CB01302;人合道。英猷獨扇。乃隆磬石。　皇心逾睠。時應刺舉。南面維蕃。相彼□
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b25"/>地。竦意祗<app source="0182009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31168;</rdg></app>。雕<note n="0182013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30984;＝晼i史】</note><app n="0182013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】"></lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30984;</rdg></app>通閣。繡柱朱門。高堂夏冷。幽室冬溫。爰圖色象。瑩磨成質。形類金山。項猶<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">朝</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b26"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">日</unclear>。<note n="0182014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30985;＝思【史】</note><app n="0182014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">思</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30985;</rdg></app>極神造。妙窮化術。真謂飛來。全同涌出。珊瑚為蓋。琉璃作<app source="0182007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">網</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08051;</rdg></app>。寶鑷搖音。靈鍾震響。樹名□
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b27"/>脫。花稱<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>想。或鄣長袪。法門遂廣。磬此誓願。　皇道重明。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear>鼓矞。神鼎不輕。官府万國。朝□
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b28"/>□靈。勒茲不朽。蘭菊其馨。　大齊太寧二年歲次壬午二月辛丑朔八日戊申。造訖故記之。
<lb ed="C I" n="0182b29"/>僕射魏收造文　元建造寺主齊輔□兒侄等　碑主安<note n="0182015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30986;＝喜【史】</note><app n="0182015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30986;</rdg></app>堤<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">陽</unclear>人小字劉永長名<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">選</unclear></p>
</div2>
